{
  "stem": "18670.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In summer time, they came out to the country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was countryside.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the back, eventually they had-- it was built during the Depression years.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had a house that was a rental property for four families, plus a caretaker, five.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we owned both of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, here's how it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At first, when my father was a custom peddler, he used to commute to the different towns.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when he finally settled there, there were-- he only came home once a week to get merchandise and so on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after a while realized-- my mother realized there were double expenses, a household in Vienna, a household in the country, and decided to move out to the country.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at that time, I was six years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My younger brother was three years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We moved out there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I started school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was an incident later on, a anti-Semitic incident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "On the way home from school, I was jumped with five other boys, came home with a black eye and told my father who had been First Sergeant in the Army seven years now-- I told my father what transpired.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And his answer was, it's impossible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Five cannot beat you up at the same time, only two at the most, maybe three.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in the future, you go to the-- for the biggest guy, draw blood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Hit him in the nose.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Poke him in the eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Draw blood, because they're all a bunch of cowards, and then run.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was the first time I was ever beaten and it was it last time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the future, I beat them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I listened to my dad and it worked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, I was almost seven years old when this happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, my father--",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
